{"tid":2188054,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美限華使節活動 京轟「反華妄想」","createTime":"2020-09-04T04:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T09:04:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dff9b11409c826b91a2aa7a946181df888dc0152","tid":2188054,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:18:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200904/JBLTHSJ6FRAXBJ7AKF45NELTVU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200904%2FJBLTHSJ6FRAXBJ7AKF45NELTVU%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=a4a20920\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200904%2FJBLTHSJ6FRAXBJ7AKF45NELTVU%2F&h=815d4b2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200904/JBLTHSJ6FRAXBJ7AKF45NELTVU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美限華使節活動 京轟「反華妄想」<br />\n<br />\n美國批評中方對美國駐華外交官設下重重障礙後，決定限制中國駐美外交人員的活動。中國外交部昨炮轟美方此舉反映美國反華勢力得到「反華妄想症」，強調中方將按形勢作出正當、必要回應，但沒提反制。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：蔡英文晤捷議長：公理正義不會不到  游錫堃受邀回訪 促議會交流<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱回應沒提反制<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人華春瑩（圖）昨在例行記者會上指，美國去年10月及今年6月，對中國駐美外交人員活動提報備要求，前日又要求中國駐美高級外交官，在探訪美國大專院校和會見美國地。。。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧前日發聲明，批評中方多年來對駐華的美國外交官施加巨大障礙，遠超外交規範。美國外交官在中國嘗試舉辦文。。。<br />\n<br />\n澎湃網"},{"pid":"4e83a4e23b997bbda1f16db01e2aeccdcfdef291","tid":2188054,"uid":259402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:19:00.000Z","msg":"反美妄想"},{"pid":"ea29b707a2d9108298fe2bcdfdbd83785fde9d16","tid":2188054,"uid":176313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:22:58.000Z","msg":"你搞人哋先啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6913a1b9129e020cf7f3b116dd613737797f1d","tid":2188054,"uid":168717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:25:12.000Z","msg":"其實有無人知 中共係咪日日都有野廢UP <br />\n睇親新聞都好似日日都有份 刷下存在感<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"